<h2><span id="1._d4_-_French_Defence">1. d4 - French Defence</span></h2>
<p>One of the more common responses to Black's intended French Defence. White creates the ideal pawn center with pawns on d4 and e4. This allows White to control the center and develop Bishops and Queen actively. The French Defence goes on with <b>2... d5</b>.
</p>
